---
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Parking Lot Striping Springfield MO | Commercial Striping, ADA & Fire Lane Markings"
  description="Commercial parking lot striping in Springfield MO for facility managers. ADA compliance, fire lanes, warehouse markings, and restriping. Same-week service across Greene County. Get a fast quote."
>
  <Header />

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center overflow-hidden">
    <img
      src="/images/hero-professional-final.jpg"
      alt="Professional technician applying crisp yellow parking lines on asphalt in Springfield Missouri"
      class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(0,0,0,.78)_0%,rgba(0,0,0,.58)_42%,rgba(0,0,0,.42)_100%)]"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pt-28 pb-20 w-full">
      <div class="max-w-3xl text-white">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-white/10 border border-white/15 rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.18em] mb-6">
          <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-brand-yellow"></span>
          Commercial-Only Parking Lot Markings
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-[0.95] mb-6">
          Commercial Parking Lot Striping in Springfield, MO
        </h1>

        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/88 leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-2xl">
          ADA-compliant markings, fire lane striping, warehouse safety lines, and professional restriping for Greene County businesses. Fast quotes. Clean documentation. No residential driveway work.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 mb-10">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary text-lg px-10 py-5 justify-center">
            Request Free Quote →
          </a>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-secondary text-lg px-10 py-5 text-center">
            Send Details Instead
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-sm text-white/90">
          <div class="bg-black/25 border border-white/10 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">✓ ADA Compliance Specialists</div>
          <div class="bg-black/25 border border-white/10 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">✓ Same-Week Availability</div>
          <div class="bg-black/25 border border-white/10 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">✓ Photo & Measurement Documentation</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TRUST + INTRO -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-14 items-start">
      <div class="lg:col-span-7 prose prose-lg max-w-none text-concrete">
        <div class="inline-block bg-brand-yellow text-primary-dark text-xs font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full tracking-[0.18em] uppercase mb-4">Springfield Commercial Specialists</div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary-dark leading-tight mb-6">Commercial Parking Lot Striping for Springfield Facility Managers, Property Managers, and Commercial Operators
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed">
          Springfield Lot Striping is built to capture one kind of lead: commercial buyers who need professional parking lot marking work done correctly, quickly, and with documentation. We are not positioned like a residential sealcoating company. We speak directly to the people who manage strip malls, office parks, truck stops, warehouse sites, apartment complexes, and retail properties across Springfield and Greene County.
        </p>
        <p>
          That matters for SEO and conversion. The current search results in this niche are filled with generic asphalt contractors, national directories, and pages that barely mention ADA, fire lanes, or warehouse markings. This site is intentionally sharper. It matches the exact search intent behind keywords like <strong>parking lot striping Springfield MO</strong>, <strong>ADA parking lot striping Springfield</strong>, and <strong>fire lane striping Springfield Missouri</strong>.
        </p>
        <p>
          We emphasize the things real buyers care about: code compliance, quick turnaround, minimal disruption to tenants, clean invoicing, and confidence that the work will hold up under Missouri weather and high-traffic commercial use.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-5 grid gap-5">
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-3xl p-8 border border-black/5">
        <div class="text-primary-dark text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.18em] font-semibold mb-3">Primary Buyers</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-dark mb-4">Who this site is built for</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-concrete">
            <li>• Facility managers under ADA deadlines</li>
            <li>• Property managers needing restriping quotes fast</li>
            <li>• General contractors needing commercial subs</li>
            <li>• Warehouse operators improving internal safety lines</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-primary-dark text-white rounded-3xl p-8">
          <div class="text-brand-yellow text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.18em] font-semibold mb-3">Coverage Area</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Greene County + nearby commercial corridors</h3>
          <p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
            Springfield, Nixa, Ozark, Republic, Battlefield, and Rogersville — including East Sunshine, Campbell Avenue, Glenstone, and the James River warehouse corridor.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICES -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-surface">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-14">
        <div class="inline-block bg-brand-yellow text-primary-dark text-xs font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full tracking-[0.18em] uppercase mb-4">Core Revenue Pages</div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary-dark mb-5">Commercial Parking Lot Striping Services in Springfield MO</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-concrete leading-relaxed">
          Every major service is broken into its own dedicated page so the site can rank for transactional local keywords instead of relying on one thin homepage to do everything.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <a href="/services/parking-lot-striping" class="group bg-white rounded-3xl overflow-hidden border border-black/5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl hover:border-brand-yellow/30 transition-all cursor-pointer">
          <img src="/images/xai_grok-imagine-image_20260623_174828_ea9e8b9b.jpg" alt="Parking lot striping service" class="h-52 w-full object-cover" />
          <div class="p-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-dark mb-4 group-hover:text-brand-yellow transition-colors">Parking Lot Striping</h3>
            <p class="text-concrete leading-relaxed">Stalls, drive aisles, crosswalks, arrows, stop bars, loading zones, and full layout refreshes for commercial lots.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/services/ada-compliance-striping" class="group bg-white rounded-3xl overflow-hidden border border-black/5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
          <img src="/images/xai_grok-imagine-image_20260623_174834_8c90e1f0.jpg" alt="ADA compliance striping service" class="h-52 w-full object-cover" />
          <div class="p-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-dark mb-4 group-hover:text-brand-yellow transition-colors">ADA Compliance Striping</h3>
            <p class="text-concrete leading-relaxed">Accessible stalls, van spaces, access aisles, compliant signage placement, and documentation for inspections.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/services/fire-lane-striping" class="group bg-white rounded-3xl overflow-hidden border border-black/5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
          <img src="/images/xai_grok-imagine-image_20260623_174841_36a1fcb1.jpg" alt="Fire lane striping service" class="h-52 w-full object-cover" />
          <div class="p-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-dark mb-4 group-hover:text-brand-yellow transition-colors">Fire Lane Striping</h3>
            <p class="text-concrete leading-relaxed">Red curb painting, white fire lane lettering, emergency access compliance, and annual refresh work.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/services/warehouse-line-striping" class="group bg-white rounded-3xl overflow-hidden border border-black/5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl hover:border-brand-yellow/30 transition-all cursor-pointer">
          <img src="/images/xai_grok-imagine-image_20260623_180942_d5ed3477.jpg" alt="Warehouse line striping service" class="h-52 w-full object-cover" />
          <div class="p-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-dark mb-4 group-hover:text-brand-yellow transition-colors">Warehouse & Loading Dock Markings</h3>
            <p class="text-concrete leading-relaxed">Forklift lanes, pedestrian walkways, dock approach markings, and internal industrial safety systems.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TRUST & BENEFITS -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-12">
        <div class="inline-block bg-brand-yellow text-primary-dark text-xs font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full tracking-[0.18em] uppercase mb-4">Built for Real Commercial Needs</div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary-dark mb-5">What Commercial Parking Lot Striping Delivers in Springfield MO</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-3xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-dark mb-4">Compliance-Ready Documentation</h3>
          <p class="text-concrete">Every job includes before/after photos, measurements, and records you can keep for insurance, tenants, or city inspections. No vague promises.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-3xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-dark mb-4">Minimal Business Disruption</h3>
          <p class="text-concrete">We schedule around your tenants and operating hours — early mornings, overnights, or weekends when possible. Most standard lots are finished the same day.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-3xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-dark mb-4">Local Commercial Focus Only</h3>
          <p class="text-concrete">Strip malls, warehouses, medical buildings, apartments, retail centers, and industrial sites across Springfield and Greene County. No residential driveways.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROCESS / PROOF -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-surface">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-14">
        <div class="inline-block bg-brand-yellow text-primary-dark text-xs font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full tracking-[0.18em] uppercase mb-4">How Jobs Get Done</div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary-dark mb-5">A process built for commercial buyers who care about compliance and speed</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8">
          <div class="text-primary-dark text-6xl font-light mb-5">01</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-dark mb-4">Assess</h3>
          <p class="text-concrete">We review lot size, current striping condition, traffic flow, ADA requirements, fire access areas, and work timing constraints.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8">
          <div class="text-primary-dark text-6xl font-light mb-5">02</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-dark mb-4">Layout</h3>
          <p class="text-concrete">We map the layout, verify stall counts, identify accessible space requirements, and plan clean execution with minimal disruption.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8">
          <div class="text-primary-dark text-6xl font-light mb-5">03</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-dark mb-4">Stripe</h3>
          <p class="text-concrete">Professional equipment, crisp lines, high-visibility paint, and clear markings for parking, ADA, fire lanes, and internal traffic zones.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8">
          <div class="text-primary-dark text-6xl font-light mb-5">04</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-dark mb-4">Document</h3>
          <p class="text-concrete">Before/after photos, measurement notes, and a clear handoff so the property manager has clean records for operations and compliance.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICE AREAS -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-14">
        <div class="inline-block bg-brand-yellow text-primary-dark text-xs font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full tracking-[0.18em] uppercase mb-4">Service Areas</div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary-dark mb-5">Built to rank beyond Springfield, not just inside it</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-concrete leading-relaxed">
          The site targets Springfield first, then supports that authority with surrounding location pages designed for adjacent commercial demand.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <a href="/service-area/springfield-mo" class="bg-surface rounded-2xl p-7 hover:bg-primary-dark hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-pointer group">
          <div class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Springfield, MO</div>
          <p class="text-sm opacity-80">East Sunshine, Campbell, Glenstone, James River warehouse corridor</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/service-area/nixa-mo" class="bg-surface rounded-2xl p-7 hover:bg-primary-dark hover:text-white transition-colors">
          <div class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Nixa, MO</div>
          <p class="text-sm opacity-80">Christian County retail, churches, medical offices, growth corridors</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/service-area/ozark-mo" class="bg-surface rounded-2xl p-7 hover:bg-primary-dark hover:text-white transition-colors">
          <div class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Ozark, MO</div>
          <p class="text-sm opacity-80">Highway 65 commercial corridor, industrial and retail properties</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/service-area/republic-mo" class="bg-surface rounded-2xl p-7 hover:bg-primary-dark hover:text-white transition-colors">
          <div class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Republic, MO</div>
          <p class="text-sm opacity-80">Western Greene County retail and industrial demand</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/service-area/battlefield-mo" class="bg-surface rounded-2xl p-7 hover:bg-primary-dark hover:text-white transition-colors">
          <div class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Battlefield, MO</div>
          <p class="text-sm opacity-80">South Springfield metro commercial and multifamily properties</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/service-area/rogersville-mo" class="bg-surface rounded-2xl p-7 hover:bg-primary-dark hover:text-white transition-colors">
          <div class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Rogersville, MO</div>
          <p class="text-sm opacity-80">Eastern Greene County business and church properties</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-primary-dark text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-14">
        <div class="inline-block bg-brand-yellow text-primary-dark text-xs font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full tracking-[0.18em] uppercase mb-4">FAQ</div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-5">Questions Springfield property managers ask before they hire</h2>
        <p class="text-white/70 text-lg">These are the practical buying questions that drive conversions and strengthen topical relevance.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <details class="bg-white/8 rounded-3xl p-8 border border-white/10">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer text-xl font-semibold">How much does parking lot striping cost in Springfield, MO?</summary>
          <p class="mt-5 text-white/80 leading-relaxed">Most standard commercial restriping work falls in the $850–$2,800 range depending on stall count, condition, and scope. Larger full layout redesigns and ADA packages are quoted separately after a site review.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-white/8 rounded-3xl p-8 border border-white/10">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer text-xl font-semibold">Do you handle ADA compliance striping and signage?</summary>
          <p class="mt-5 text-white/80 leading-relaxed">Yes. Accessible stall counts, van spaces, access aisles, signage placement, and supporting documentation are all part of our ADA-focused service offering.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-white/8 rounded-3xl p-8 border border-white/10">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer text-xl font-semibold">Can striping be scheduled without disrupting tenants?</summary>
          <p class="mt-5 text-white/80 leading-relaxed">That is usually the goal. Many jobs are scheduled in early morning, evening, or phased windows so tenants, truck traffic, and customers can keep moving.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-white/8 rounded-3xl p-8 border border-white/10">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer text-xl font-semibold">What kinds of commercial properties do you serve?</summary>
          <p class="mt-5 text-white/80 leading-relaxed">Strip malls, office parks, warehouse sites, apartment complexes, truck stops, retail chains, churches, schools, and commercial mixed-use properties throughout Greene County.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-white/8 rounded-3xl p-8 border border-white/10">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer text-xl font-semibold">How often should a commercial lot be restriped?</summary>
          <p class="mt-5 text-white/80 leading-relaxed">In this market, many properties need fresh striping every 18–24 months. High-traffic sites or properties exposed to heavy weathering may need it sooner.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FINAL CTA -->
  <section id="quote" class="py-24 bg-brand-yellow">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <div class="text-primary-dark text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] mb-4">Get a Quote</div>
          <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold text-primary-dark mb-6 leading-tight">Need commercial striping done right the first time?</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-primary-dark/80 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Tell us about your lot, property type, and service need. Whether it is ADA work, fire lane updates, warehouse safety lines, or a full restripe, this site is built to turn that demand into fast qualified calls.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
            <a href="/contact" class="text-brand-yellow hover:underline" class="bg-primary-dark hover:bg-black text-white text-lg font-semibold px-10 py-5 rounded-2xl transition-colors text-center">
              Open Quote Form
            </a>
            <a href="/contact" class="text-brand-yellow hover:underline" class="border-2 border-primary-dark text-primary-dark hover:bg-primary-dark hover:text-white text-lg font-semibold px-10 py-5 rounded-2xl transition-colors text-center">
              Open Contact Form
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl">
          <div class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-brand-yellow font-semibold mb-4">What to include</div>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-concrete">
            <li>• Property type (strip mall, office park, warehouse, etc.)</li>
            <li>• Approximate number of spaces or lot size</li>
            <li>• Service needed: restriping, ADA, fire lane, warehouse, or layout redesign</li>
            <li>• Whether the work needs to happen during off-hours</li>
            <li>• Any compliance or inspection deadline</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="bg-primary-dark text-white/80 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
      <div>
        <img src="/images/logo-final-v2.png" alt="Springfield Lot Striping" class="h-12 mb-6 brightness-125" />
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed">Commercial parking lot striping, ADA compliance markings, fire lane striping, warehouse safety lines, and restriping for Springfield and surrounding service areas.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="font-semibold text-brand-yellow mb-5 uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-sm">Top Pages</p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/services/parking-lot-striping" class="text-brand-yellow hover:underline" class="hover:text-white">Parking Lot Striping</a></li>
          <li><a href="/services/ada-compliance-striping" class="hover:text-white">ADA Compliance</a></li>
          <li><a href="/services/fire-lane-striping" class="hover:text-white">Fire Lane Striping</a></li>
          <li><a href="/service-area/springfield-mo" class="text-brand-yellow hover:underline" class="hover:text-white">Springfield Service Area</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog" class="hover:text-white">Blog & Guides</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="font-semibold text-brand-yellow mb-5 uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-sm">Contact</p>
        <p class="text-lg font-medium text-white">Use the quote form for fast callback scheduling.</p>
        <p class="text-sm mt-2">Springfield, Missouri</p>
        <p class="text-sm mt-4">Commercial-focused lead generation site for parking lot striping and compliance services.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 border-t border-white/10 mt-12 pt-8 text-xs opacity-55">
      © 2026 Springfield Lot Striping. Built for commercial parking lot striping lead generation in Springfield, MO.
    </div>
  </footer>
</BaseLayout>
